WEBVTT

01:35.700 --> 01:39.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:39.980 --> 01:42.980
[Episode 5]

01:43.400 --> 01:44.260
Demons may not stir up trouble,

01:44.790 --> 01:45.460
but humans can.

01:51.120 --> 01:51.690
Luo Wei,

01:52.350 --> 01:53.380
you're worse than a demon.

01:54.870 --> 01:57.130
One, two, three, four.

01:57.510 --> 01:58.460
These four things

01:58.840 --> 01:59.570
are the keys

01:59.920 --> 02:01.130
to tonight's

02:01.230 --> 02:02.330
fox demon murder case.

02:03.400 --> 02:04.330
Ji, you're amazing!

02:04.790 --> 02:05.770
Stop keeping us in suspense.

02:06.040 --> 02:06.660
Spill it.

02:08.070 --> 02:08.880
After Wei Qing died,

02:08.880 --> 02:10.720
it's obvious Ms. Yu planned

02:10.720 --> 02:11.980
to leave immediately.

02:12.520 --> 02:13.660
In the bags she packed,

02:13.830 --> 02:15.290
besides her own clothes,

02:15.960 --> 02:17.340
there were also Steward Luo's.

02:18.120 --> 02:18.690
So,

02:19.000 --> 02:19.780
Ms. Yu was planning

02:19.800 --> 02:21.380
to run away with you,

02:22.000 --> 02:22.660
right?

02:24.680 --> 02:25.600
But Yu Shengwei

02:25.630 --> 02:26.980
is from a respectable family.

02:27.310 --> 02:28.260
If she suddenly vanished,

02:28.630 --> 02:30.220
the Yus would report it,

02:30.400 --> 02:31.340
and search the entire city.

02:32.080 --> 02:33.830
So how could she

02:34.360 --> 02:36.170
completely escape this place?

02:37.800 --> 02:38.940
I know you don't love him.

02:40.000 --> 02:41.690
If it weren't for that talisman,

02:42.430 --> 02:43.820
you'd never have married him.

02:47.960 --> 02:49.500
I don't want to be trapped

02:49.840 --> 02:50.780
in this mansion for life.

02:56.560 --> 02:57.330
Wherever you go,

02:58.000 --> 02:58.900
I'll follow.

03:00.560 --> 03:01.850
But if you disappear,

03:03.190 --> 03:04.380
your family and the authorities

03:06.280 --> 03:07.260
will come looking.

03:12.080 --> 03:12.780
I have a plan.

03:14.630 --> 03:16.130
To vanish completely,

03:17.560 --> 03:18.410
you must first die.

03:19.120 --> 03:20.060
Fake your death to get away.

03:20.590 --> 03:21.340
Nice and clean.

03:22.080 --> 03:23.100
That's a really good plan.

03:23.400 --> 03:23.980
Smart.

03:24.710 --> 03:26.500
But Ms. Yu is even smarter.

03:26.800 --> 03:27.890
She perfectly used

03:27.910 --> 03:29.340
the fox demon chaos in the mansion

03:29.840 --> 03:30.940
to make everyone believe

03:31.120 --> 03:32.690
she died at its claws.

03:48.000 --> 03:49.660
So the fox demon shadow

03:50.360 --> 03:51.890
we saw outside her room?

04:09.710 --> 04:11.190
They planned

04:11.240 --> 04:13.370
to use shadow play to lure us away,

04:13.540 --> 04:15.100
sending everyone after the fox demon.

04:19.150 --> 04:19.570
That way,

04:19.840 --> 04:20.650
they could

04:20.750 --> 04:22.580
sneak away without a trace.

04:22.920 --> 04:24.660
When we returned and found no body,

04:24.720 --> 04:25.810
we'd be helpless,

04:26.120 --> 04:28.010
only able to assume the fox demon took her

04:28.160 --> 04:28.980
or ate her.

04:31.600 --> 04:32.880
Pulling a stunt

04:32.880 --> 04:34.660
right under our noses,

04:35.040 --> 04:36.580
two fox demons?

04:37.630 --> 04:38.660
Trying to teach a master?

04:40.390 --> 04:40.980
No.

04:41.630 --> 04:43.810
Trying to fool Li Jie!

04:44.070 --> 04:44.580
Thanks.

04:44.920 --> 04:45.610
You're welcome.

04:48.630 --> 04:49.290
Sit up straight.

04:50.060 --> 04:51.050
Look at you.

04:53.830 --> 04:54.660
So mean!

04:55.270 --> 04:56.050
And you.

05:11.800 --> 05:12.410
Anything else?

05:14.000 --> 05:15.140
Yes!

05:16.430 --> 05:17.220
Next,

05:17.430 --> 05:18.370
how did they manage

05:18.390 --> 05:19.700
to lure the people from the front courtyard

05:19.720 --> 05:20.540
away too?

05:20.830 --> 05:21.730
Do you remember

05:22.120 --> 05:24.730
what Ms. Yu is best at embroidering?

05:25.120 --> 05:26.810
She's Luo'an's famous embroiderer,

05:27.630 --> 05:28.410
especially skilled at stitching

05:29.040 --> 05:30.140
birds and beasts.

05:30.800 --> 05:31.540
Birds and beasts.

05:32.070 --> 05:32.700
Exactly.

05:33.310 --> 05:33.780
Here.

05:48.850 --> 05:50.070
Before everyone gathered

05:50.070 --> 05:51.340
in the front yard for the ceremony,

05:51.630 --> 05:53.730
Steward Luo had already hung up

05:53.730 --> 05:54.940
this cloth with a fox there.

06:00.560 --> 06:02.770
Then, she just needed to lure everyone over

06:02.800 --> 06:04.740
to see the fox demon with their own eyes.

06:05.160 --> 06:05.900
A fox demon...

06:07.040 --> 06:08.170
It's a fox demon!

06:16.310 --> 06:18.270
But when we got to the dye workshop,

06:18.560 --> 06:20.100
we didn't see that cloth.

06:20.870 --> 06:22.610
Unlike a man's feelings,

06:23.120 --> 06:24.410
it couldn't just disappear

06:24.950 --> 06:26.250
in the blink of an eye.

06:27.920 --> 06:29.350
Not every man's feelings

06:29.360 --> 06:30.700
disappear in a blink.

06:32.360 --> 06:33.050
Really?

06:34.950 --> 06:35.580
This piece here

06:35.800 --> 06:36.980
is the black cloth with the fox

06:37.120 --> 06:38.020
Ms. Yu embroidered.

06:41.630 --> 06:42.400
Where's the fox?

06:43.360 --> 06:45.250
This is Steward Luo's smartest move.

06:45.870 --> 06:46.990
She really did make the fox

06:46.990 --> 06:48.110
disappear in a blink.

06:50.270 --> 06:52.130
So Steward Luo can use demon magic?

06:52.510 --> 06:53.500
Nothing to do with magic.

06:54.120 --> 06:54.930
It's the kite.

06:57.480 --> 06:58.580
What a huge kite!

07:01.120 --> 07:02.290
Back in my hometown,

07:02.830 --> 07:04.410
they say when bad things happen,

07:04.750 --> 07:06.340
we should buy a kite and fly it away.

07:07.270 --> 07:08.490
The higher the kite flies,

07:08.830 --> 07:10.980
the further the bad luck goes.

07:32.560 --> 07:34.700
The kite flew away with threads

07:34.870 --> 07:36.140
from the embroidery.

07:36.240 --> 07:37.150
The silver threads

07:37.160 --> 07:38.300
were pulled out bit by bit.

07:38.920 --> 07:41.020
So the fox demon naturally vanished.

07:41.500 --> 07:42.170
Indeed.

07:42.750 --> 07:44.270
This cloth is covered

07:44.390 --> 07:45.370
in needle holes.

07:56.750 --> 07:57.540
Interesting.

08:00.430 --> 08:02.250
Two mortals went to great lengths

08:02.270 --> 08:03.340
to set up a fake fox demon,

08:04.240 --> 08:05.250
never expecting

08:05.720 --> 08:07.170
the real one to show up.

08:08.070 --> 08:09.140
Xiaowei,

08:10.680 --> 08:11.980
were you helping them?

08:12.750 --> 08:14.220
I just wanted to hold you off...

08:16.630 --> 08:18.370
to buy Shengwei some time.

08:19.310 --> 08:20.020
But in the end,

08:21.040 --> 08:21.930
you only hurt her.

08:24.430 --> 08:25.850
People with evil hearts

08:26.560 --> 08:28.850
are scarier than demons.

08:29.370 --> 08:30.140
You...

08:32.240 --> 08:33.370
Don't you dare slander me!

08:33.980 --> 08:34.900
A fox demon killed Ms. Yu

08:34.920 --> 08:35.870
and ripped out her heart!

08:36.720 --> 08:37.460
You're so stubborn.

08:38.550 --> 08:40.010
In denial even with the proof right there.

08:40.600 --> 08:41.650
Ms. Yu's wounds

08:42.120 --> 08:43.820
were clearly made by a demon's claws.

08:45.840 --> 08:46.750
That's because

08:47.080 --> 08:48.730
the murder weapon you used is special.

08:49.250 --> 08:50.350
You're really clever.

08:51.570 --> 08:53.350
After you led us to the dye workshop,

08:53.600 --> 08:54.890
you went straight to Ms. Yu.

08:55.520 --> 08:56.180
A fox demon!

08:56.880 --> 08:57.980
It's at the dye workshop!

09:42.440 --> 09:42.980
Let's go!

09:44.920 --> 09:45.750
Go?

10:00.030 --> 10:01.530
I don't want to be left with nothing again.

10:02.790 --> 10:04.250
I don't want to start over.

10:06.240 --> 10:08.010
I don't want to be homeless anymore.

10:09.670 --> 10:11.980
You kept making me...

10:13.000 --> 10:14.730
my favorite chestnut cake,

10:15.000 --> 10:16.460
just to make me happy,

10:17.120 --> 10:17.890
didn't you?

10:18.720 --> 10:19.460
And...

10:20.360 --> 10:22.490
you prepared cakes for me,

10:23.630 --> 10:25.370
and put them in my bag...

10:30.030 --> 10:31.050
Actually,

10:31.790 --> 10:35.400
you wanted to come with me...

10:39.000 --> 10:40.420
What are you talking about?

10:47.480 --> 10:48.360
I never prepared

10:48.360 --> 10:50.060
any chestnut cake for you.

10:51.870 --> 10:53.220
What I've been preparing

10:54.080 --> 10:55.460
is something else.

10:58.080 --> 10:59.060
All along,

11:01.440 --> 11:03.490
I've been copying Wei Qing's handwriting.

11:04.510 --> 11:05.980
Using his handwriting,

11:06.600 --> 11:08.010
I wrote a contract.

11:08.910 --> 11:10.460
Now that he's dead,

11:11.720 --> 11:12.980
if you die too,

11:13.790 --> 11:15.130
the entire Wei cloth business

11:15.150 --> 11:16.460
will be mine.

12:14.080 --> 12:14.850
Too bad

12:15.720 --> 12:16.850
you were so nervous

12:17.440 --> 12:19.220
you forgot about the heated red candle.

12:19.870 --> 12:21.370
Even a light touch

12:22.510 --> 12:23.730
would leave a mark on it.

12:26.120 --> 12:27.060
Need me to match

12:27.120 --> 12:28.100
the fingerprints on it,

12:28.390 --> 12:29.220
Steward Luo?

12:40.720 --> 12:41.610
- It was you! - What?

12:41.790 --> 12:43.410
You killed Shengwei!

12:43.750 --> 12:45.250
You killed Shengwei!

12:55.200 --> 12:55.950
The waning moon mark!

12:58.270 --> 12:58.820
No.

12:59.440 --> 13:00.850
It's just a similar tattoo.

13:01.240 --> 13:02.770
I was born with this mark.

13:03.870 --> 13:04.730
We agreed to become

13:04.730 --> 13:05.700
sworn sisters, right?

13:06.670 --> 13:07.580
Then I'll get one too.

13:08.550 --> 13:10.250
You don't deserve it!

13:19.550 --> 13:21.340
I really don't.

13:24.720 --> 13:27.370
You're powerful demon hunters,

13:29.060 --> 13:31.560
wealthy nobles from prestigious families.

13:35.080 --> 13:37.340
Have you ever known hunger and cold,

13:38.390 --> 13:39.820
been bullied every day,

13:39.840 --> 13:41.770
and trampled upon?

13:46.910 --> 13:49.320
The Shilin Sect preaches protecting the people,

13:49.320 --> 13:50.510
loving all living beings.

13:52.200 --> 13:53.300
Then let me ask you,

13:54.840 --> 13:55.940
don't the folks

13:57.720 --> 13:59.060
in the old town count?

14:08.960 --> 14:10.940
The wailing there never stops.

14:10.960 --> 14:12.490
You don't hear it?

14:26.030 --> 14:27.490
But Ms. Yu never bullied you.

14:28.390 --> 14:30.100
She even pulled you from the pit.

14:30.840 --> 14:31.890
No matter how bitter you feel,

14:32.840 --> 14:34.220
she doesn't deserve your hatred.

14:34.840 --> 14:37.080
I just don't want to be living

14:37.080 --> 14:38.400
in fear again.

14:40.320 --> 14:41.420
I didn't want to give up

14:41.420 --> 14:42.980
the wealth and comfort before me.

14:46.030 --> 14:47.060
Was that wrong?

14:51.750 --> 14:52.530
Yes.

14:56.550 --> 14:57.490
But I accept that.

15:01.320 --> 15:02.590
Those who've been rained on

15:03.320 --> 15:05.110
should be more willing to lend an umbrella.

15:06.550 --> 15:07.340
However...

15:08.320 --> 15:10.400
you kept for yourself the umbrella

15:10.750 --> 15:11.650
kindly lent to you.

15:12.480 --> 15:13.460
Even demons are grateful.

15:15.000 --> 15:16.060
You're worse than a demon.

15:18.480 --> 15:19.980
The world is cold and bleak.

15:22.360 --> 15:23.880
A caring heart is hard to find.

15:25.150 --> 15:27.580
I've been searching for that caring heart

15:28.360 --> 15:29.700
in the vast sea of people,

15:30.030 --> 15:31.100
lifetime after lifetime.

15:31.870 --> 15:33.420
The pain is unbearable.

15:39.080 --> 15:39.850
But you...

15:41.720 --> 15:43.150
you killed the one

15:43.150 --> 15:44.920
who truly cared for you.

15:57.320 --> 15:58.650
After hundreds of years,

16:01.910 --> 16:03.070
I still don't get

16:06.180 --> 16:08.580
the human heart.

16:24.420 --> 16:26.660
[Gift Register]

16:27.670 --> 16:28.490
What's this?

16:29.150 --> 16:30.850
The list Xiaowei put a death curse on.

16:32.510 --> 16:33.370
She gave it to me.

16:36.620 --> 16:37.860
[Gift Register]

16:48.080 --> 16:48.890
It's gone!

16:49.440 --> 16:50.150
Look!

16:55.120 --> 16:56.170
Look, it's gone!

16:56.170 --> 16:58.070
It vanished!

16:58.790 --> 16:59.460
Let me taste something.

17:03.920 --> 17:05.220
So fragrant!

17:05.550 --> 17:06.640
Here, great master,

17:07.480 --> 17:08.250
try some too.

17:13.270 --> 17:13.940
Right?

17:18.160 --> 17:19.220
What about Luo Wei?

17:19.780 --> 17:21.310
She's handed over to the authorities.

17:22.790 --> 17:23.620
And Xiaowei?

17:26.030 --> 17:27.300
People say

17:28.790 --> 17:30.980
scent is the longest-lasting memory.

17:34.110 --> 17:35.770
But I've already forgotten...

17:38.290 --> 17:39.840
how long it's been

17:41.590 --> 17:43.290
since I last smelled flowers.

17:43.290 --> 17:48.340
♪Twilight drifts through bustling streets♪

17:49.100 --> 17:54.260
♪Thick snow traps all the past in sheets♪

17:55.020 --> 18:00.940
♪Only with closed eyes, I see your face♪

18:01.140 --> 18:05.460
♪Red-rimmed eyes hide so many unsaid...♪

18:05.480 --> 18:06.810
I will never

18:07.830 --> 18:09.330
smell flowers again.

18:13.020 --> 18:18.460
♪Shining through my fearful flight...♪

18:20.790 --> 18:22.610
I've smelled spring blooms and autumn grass,

18:23.590 --> 18:25.070
rain, snow, wind, frost.

18:26.480 --> 18:28.180
I've smelled the world's delicacies,

18:29.270 --> 18:30.700
the warm breath of daily life.

18:32.440 --> 18:33.730
That was when

18:36.680 --> 18:38.180
I felt most like a human.

18:40.030 --> 18:41.220
Too bad later,

18:42.350 --> 18:43.860
I couldn't smell anything anymore.

18:46.110 --> 18:47.390
I wanted to offer you

18:47.390 --> 18:49.400
the very best of this world.

18:51.110 --> 18:51.940
I never imagined

18:52.880 --> 18:54.900
a simple piece of chestnut cake

18:55.030 --> 18:56.510
could make you so happy.

18:57.960 --> 18:59.730
Your joy was so simple,

19:00.200 --> 19:01.490
yet I couldn't protect it.

19:02.880 --> 19:03.980
For hundreds of years,

19:06.200 --> 19:07.490
lifetime after lifetime,

19:08.550 --> 19:10.330
I always wanted to keep you safe.

19:11.400 --> 19:12.330
But now,

19:13.590 --> 19:14.900
I've only harmed you.

19:40.200 --> 19:41.250
Using magic again?

19:42.240 --> 19:43.010
She wants to die?

20:29.310 --> 20:30.250
Wu...
[*mist]

20:34.440 --> 20:35.380
Lu...
[*dew]

20:45.480 --> 20:46.330
Wu...
[*mist]

20:52.590 --> 20:53.420
Lu...
[*dew]

20:56.440 --> 20:57.140
Lu...
[*dew]

21:23.880 --> 21:24.570
Thank you.

21:30.200 --> 21:31.490
The world is cold and bleak.

21:32.480 --> 21:33.380
A caring heart is hard to find.

21:34.440 --> 21:36.330
You can capture the form, but never the heart.

21:39.240 --> 21:39.940
What a pity.

21:42.400 --> 21:43.530
You feel sorry for Xiaowei?

21:46.000 --> 21:48.010
Few hunters sympathize with demons.

21:49.680 --> 21:50.740
Under the sun,

21:51.350 --> 21:52.420
all beings suffer.

21:53.640 --> 21:55.100
When I see something heartbreaking,

21:56.110 --> 21:57.050
I feel sympathy.

21:58.270 --> 21:59.760
Demons can seduce hearts,

22:00.270 --> 22:01.500
but can hardly understand them.

22:03.480 --> 22:04.670
People always say

22:04.720 --> 22:06.290
demons are cruel and cold-blooded,

22:06.830 --> 22:07.650
but they don't know

22:08.350 --> 22:10.140
some are deeply obsessed with love.

22:11.750 --> 22:13.290
Yu Shengwei is just Yu Shengwei.

22:14.880 --> 22:16.370
She's no longer Wang Sheng.

22:17.440 --> 22:18.660
She doesn't know Xiaowei,

22:19.350 --> 22:20.420
never saved Xiaowei either.

22:21.480 --> 22:22.940
Xiaowei's deep affection

22:24.440 --> 22:26.150
is nothing but a pipe dream.

22:26.550 --> 22:28.440
Even exhausting a thousand years of magic,

22:29.400 --> 22:30.350
you can save the person,

22:32.160 --> 22:33.250
but not the heart.

22:34.510 --> 22:36.380
He's trapped by his own obsession,

22:37.160 --> 22:39.250
mistaking gratitude for love.

22:39.920 --> 22:41.770
Few demons truly understand love.

22:43.440 --> 22:44.530
With all that talk,

22:45.550 --> 22:47.550
you seem to know love pretty well.

22:49.270 --> 22:50.090
Of course.

22:51.440 --> 22:52.730
So who loves you enough

22:52.920 --> 22:54.290
to die for you?

22:58.880 --> 22:59.380
Anyone?

23:05.160 --> 23:06.490
Run, child!

23:08.440 --> 23:09.980
You must survive!

23:25.790 --> 23:26.730
I never thought

23:27.920 --> 23:29.970
someone would truly die for love.

23:31.160 --> 23:32.330
They say blood and tears

23:33.750 --> 23:34.620
are hot.

23:36.240 --> 23:37.710
Never thought one day

23:38.640 --> 23:40.920
I'd see tears turn to ice.

23:44.000 --> 23:45.270
Demons' tears

23:45.960 --> 23:46.860
are all fake,

23:48.920 --> 23:50.570
just to make themselves

23:50.590 --> 23:51.660
look more human.

23:53.440 --> 23:54.570
I really don't get it.

23:55.590 --> 23:56.730
Why are so many demons

23:57.590 --> 23:58.290
painting bones,

23:59.110 --> 23:59.940
painting skin,

24:01.510 --> 24:02.460
desperate to be human?

24:20.440 --> 24:21.090
Wangyan,

24:24.070 --> 24:25.900
are you sad for Xiaowei?

24:27.270 --> 24:29.180
I'm just recalling a lot of the past.

24:30.830 --> 24:32.050
Since birth,

24:32.590 --> 24:33.730
our Nine-Tailed clan

24:34.310 --> 24:36.490
have cultivated under the Fox Queen.

24:37.000 --> 24:38.890
She taught us like a mother,

24:39.310 --> 24:40.640
taking us along

24:41.160 --> 24:44.060
to find colorful stones for Goddess Nuwa.

24:44.960 --> 24:46.180
After the Fox Queen passed,

24:47.200 --> 24:49.420
Goddess Nuwa channeled the moon's power,

24:50.030 --> 24:51.860
granting us, the Fox Queen's descendants,

24:51.880 --> 24:53.460
the power of endless rebirth.

24:54.110 --> 24:54.770
From then on,

24:55.400 --> 24:56.490
we formed

24:57.110 --> 24:58.010
the Formless Moon Sect,

24:59.160 --> 25:02.010
guarding the Oracle Stone left by Nuwa.

25:04.350 --> 25:06.140
I thought with immortality,

25:07.480 --> 25:08.090
we sisters

25:08.110 --> 25:09.900
would never suffer separation again.

25:12.000 --> 25:13.660
But Xiaowei still left.

25:15.750 --> 25:17.470
Reunited after a hundred years,

25:18.160 --> 25:19.660
it just ends up like this.

25:21.030 --> 25:22.330
Xiaowei was so silly.

25:23.070 --> 25:24.330
Fleeing the sect,

25:25.590 --> 25:27.010
enduring the pain of losing her tail,

25:28.880 --> 25:29.980
and living in hiding

25:31.960 --> 25:33.290
just to stay by one person.

25:34.480 --> 25:35.940
For even the simplest things,

25:36.110 --> 25:37.420
she couldn't use magic,

25:38.110 --> 25:39.490
ending up covered in wounds.

25:40.640 --> 25:41.650
Those chestnut cakes

25:41.650 --> 25:42.860
were all made by her own hands.

25:43.920 --> 25:45.260
Just like an ordinary person,

25:45.750 --> 25:47.860
she sliced chestnuts piece by piece,

25:48.310 --> 25:50.850
mashing them into paste,

25:51.200 --> 25:52.140
and making cakes.

25:53.510 --> 25:55.330
Like cutting open her own heart,

25:56.030 --> 25:57.810
just to make her lover happy.

25:58.550 --> 26:00.220
And this is how it ended.

26:01.830 --> 26:03.290
Love in this world...

26:06.510 --> 26:07.460
better off without it.

26:09.480 --> 26:10.250
Yeah.

26:11.350 --> 26:12.530
Love in this world

26:13.510 --> 26:15.220
really is complicated.

26:19.680 --> 26:20.860
Don't worry.

26:21.480 --> 26:23.090
I'll never betray you

26:23.480 --> 26:24.530
or our sect.

26:38.070 --> 26:39.220
Wangyan,

26:39.830 --> 26:41.140
you wouldn't either, right?

26:44.960 --> 26:46.690
I don't understand love,

26:46.960 --> 26:47.860
nor hate.

26:49.590 --> 26:51.380
I don't think I've ever loved anyone,

26:51.880 --> 26:53.770
or hated anyone either.

26:55.350 --> 26:56.360
I guess

26:56.720 --> 26:57.720
I'm just...

26:57.720 --> 26:58.290
A woodenhead.

27:00.400 --> 27:01.450
When a guy

27:01.680 --> 27:02.580
is clueless

27:02.830 --> 27:04.180
and don't get romance,

27:05.070 --> 27:06.330
young girls call him a woodenhead.

27:07.720 --> 27:08.330
Fine,

27:09.200 --> 27:10.330
I'm a woodenhead then.

27:11.110 --> 27:11.940
No, you're not.

27:13.000 --> 27:14.050
I think Miss Lu Wuyi

27:14.070 --> 27:14.860
is more like one.

27:19.000 --> 27:19.900
Miss Lu?

27:21.440 --> 27:22.330
Miss Lu...

27:22.920 --> 27:23.700
is clever.

27:24.480 --> 27:25.730
Then she's pretending to be dumb.

27:26.750 --> 27:27.770
You like her so much.

27:28.200 --> 27:29.330
Even a woodenhead can see it.

27:38.640 --> 27:39.700
Is it that obvious?

27:42.550 --> 27:43.050
Oh man.

27:44.790 --> 27:45.750
Miss Wu said

27:46.270 --> 27:47.770
they're taking Xiaowei back.

27:47.790 --> 27:48.420
That won't do!

27:48.550 --> 27:49.140
Xiaowei still owes...

27:52.510 --> 27:53.220
Xiaowei

27:53.640 --> 27:55.050
is coming with us.

27:55.640 --> 27:57.410
Can you beat Lu Wuyi and Wu Wangyan?

27:58.830 --> 28:00.250
You and me

28:01.880 --> 28:03.460
are a match for them, right?

28:04.720 --> 28:05.620
It's just...

28:07.550 --> 28:08.980
I don't want to fight Miss Lu.

28:09.880 --> 28:11.220
In your dreams, you're a match.

28:12.350 --> 28:13.460
I'll help you bring Xiaowei

28:13.480 --> 28:14.380
to the Shilin Sect.

28:17.030 --> 28:18.050
Why would you help?

28:18.880 --> 28:20.040
I was hunting Xiaowei

28:20.590 --> 28:21.700
for the bounty anyway.

28:22.240 --> 28:23.050
Didn't they say,

28:23.550 --> 28:24.860
catch the heart-ripping killer,

28:25.510 --> 28:27.220
and you get into the Shilin Sect?

28:28.920 --> 28:30.220
So you want to join the Shilin Sect?

28:30.640 --> 28:32.050
That's easy for me to arrange.

28:34.000 --> 28:34.830
Oh? So you have

28:34.830 --> 28:35.980
such a high status

28:36.030 --> 28:36.700
in the Shilin Sect?

28:39.160 --> 28:39.880
His words?

28:40.510 --> 28:42.150
Half of it is trash.

28:42.550 --> 28:43.960
Count yourself lucky

28:44.440 --> 28:46.180
if you can scrape together a couple of truths.

28:52.750 --> 28:53.250
But if you

28:53.270 --> 28:54.660
really can bring Xiaowei to us,

28:56.000 --> 28:57.420
getting into the sect shouldn't be a problem.

29:00.160 --> 29:00.980
Give it back first.

29:02.920 --> 29:03.490
Give what?

29:04.270 --> 29:05.140
It's on you.

29:06.270 --> 29:06.940
I can smell it.

29:13.480 --> 29:15.290
You mean this Cosmic Pouch

29:15.590 --> 29:16.660
and the little demon within?

29:17.590 --> 29:18.720
No need to trouble you.

29:19.030 --> 29:19.710
We'll just

29:19.710 --> 29:21.140
take him back with us.

29:21.400 --> 29:22.330
If we find

29:22.330 --> 29:23.870
no evil deeds from him,

29:24.030 --> 29:26.140
we'll keep him as a pet.

29:28.030 --> 29:29.430
He's even biting through the bag?

29:33.000 --> 29:33.810
That's a dog.

29:37.920 --> 29:38.880
A demon hunter

29:38.880 --> 29:40.290
carrying a demon around?

29:41.160 --> 29:41.940
Are you crazy?

29:42.160 --> 29:42.860
Nonsense!

29:43.440 --> 29:44.140
Young man,

29:44.480 --> 29:45.620
quit calling me a demon.

29:45.880 --> 29:46.660
It sounds awful.

29:47.000 --> 29:47.620
Me,

29:48.350 --> 29:49.220
I'm family with him,

29:49.440 --> 29:50.050
buddies with him.

29:50.680 --> 29:51.570
More like a follower.

29:53.720 --> 29:54.220
So...

29:54.480 --> 29:56.380
you're a weasel's follower?

29:57.920 --> 29:58.660
That's rough.

29:59.720 --> 30:00.980
No wonder you want to join our sect.

30:01.550 --> 30:02.140
Enough.

30:02.440 --> 30:03.250
Save him some face.

30:03.440 --> 30:04.730
He's my follower!

30:05.070 --> 30:06.730
I need a spy, an accomplice...

30:08.750 --> 30:09.420
Well, a helper.

30:10.000 --> 30:11.010
What's wrong with that?

30:11.680 --> 30:12.330
Nothing.

30:13.110 --> 30:13.700
True.

30:14.030 --> 30:14.710
After all,

30:14.710 --> 30:16.330
weasels always live in packs,

30:16.440 --> 30:18.080
sneaking around everywhere,

30:18.190 --> 30:19.810
best at sniffing out gossip.

30:20.000 --> 30:21.010
Perfect for a spy.

30:21.750 --> 30:22.330
Li Jie,

30:22.550 --> 30:23.670
when we get back,

30:23.790 --> 30:25.430
let's get a captured weasel

30:25.480 --> 30:26.090
to switch sides.

30:26.350 --> 30:27.330
Seems useful.

30:27.720 --> 30:28.620
I heard that!

30:29.830 --> 30:31.050
Both my ears heard it!

30:31.480 --> 30:33.050
Your ears are so small!

30:34.680 --> 30:35.380
Li Jie, look...

30:38.440 --> 30:39.290
His are even smaller.

30:43.960 --> 30:44.490
Little mouse.

30:44.920 --> 30:46.490
You weasels all come in packs.

30:46.640 --> 30:47.390
You got names?

30:47.590 --> 30:48.730
How rude!

30:49.640 --> 30:50.330
Little mouse?

30:51.750 --> 30:52.700
Among humans,

30:53.240 --> 30:54.960
we're called the Yellow Spirit.

30:55.640 --> 30:57.320
And we name ourselves carefully.

30:57.830 --> 30:59.050
Our elders use the first thing

30:59.200 --> 30:59.860
we steal

31:00.070 --> 31:01.010
to name us.

31:02.220 --> 31:03.200
And

31:03.400 --> 31:04.860
the first thing I ever got

31:05.350 --> 31:06.290
was a ruler.

31:06.830 --> 31:07.420
Plus,

31:07.590 --> 31:08.320
we're weasels.

31:08.440 --> 31:09.090
So, you're "Ruler Weasel"?

31:10.200 --> 31:11.360
What's that thing?

31:12.510 --> 31:13.220
Ridiculous!

31:14.400 --> 31:14.980
Who'd have such

31:15.110 --> 31:16.050
a lousy name?

31:16.640 --> 31:17.330
My surname is You,
[*weasel]

31:17.750 --> 31:19.090
and my given name is Chi.
[*ruler]

31:19.830 --> 31:20.570
Catchy, right?

31:23.680 --> 31:24.530
Yeah...

31:25.350 --> 31:26.140
Very catchy.

31:37.480 --> 31:38.180
Miss Lu.

31:42.160 --> 31:42.730
Stop right there.

31:45.110 --> 31:45.980
Want to go in?

31:48.000 --> 31:48.940
No, you can't.

31:50.030 --> 31:51.730
Xiaowei is from our Formless Moon Sect.

31:52.160 --> 31:53.810
You can't take him.

31:55.510 --> 31:56.210
Ji,

31:56.640 --> 31:57.680
you're such a nice guy.

31:58.200 --> 31:59.660
Don't make me fight you, okay?

32:00.750 --> 32:01.700
You already fought.

32:03.270 --> 32:04.570
Check with its master before hitting the dog.

32:05.160 --> 32:05.940
With just you?

32:06.920 --> 32:07.730
You've got it backwards.

32:08.440 --> 32:10.980
Two lousy hunters from the Shilin Sect,

32:12.240 --> 32:13.810
not a single flower on your foreheads,

32:14.200 --> 32:16.430
wanting to take someone from us?

32:16.790 --> 32:17.620
Or...

32:18.000 --> 32:18.900
do you have

32:18.900 --> 32:20.440
some other noble status?

32:27.070 --> 32:27.530
So rude.

32:28.680 --> 32:29.420
Watch this.

32:33.830 --> 32:34.460
Miss Lu,

32:34.920 --> 32:36.730
we're old acquaintances,

32:37.350 --> 32:38.980
and have a little connection.

32:39.640 --> 32:40.940
Just do me a small favor.

32:41.350 --> 32:42.700
Let me talk to Xiaowei alone.

32:43.240 --> 32:43.810
Can you?

32:45.160 --> 32:46.350
You want to talk?

32:49.240 --> 32:50.490
What's in it for me?

32:53.680 --> 32:55.050
What do you want?

32:55.270 --> 32:55.860
Name it.

32:59.750 --> 33:01.700
That ugly doll you always carry.

33:02.350 --> 33:03.090
Give it to me.

33:03.640 --> 33:04.250
How about that?

33:04.880 --> 33:05.660
No, no way!

33:06.880 --> 33:07.980
What's ugly about it?

33:09.110 --> 33:09.770
Miss Lu,

33:10.790 --> 33:11.980
I'll give you anything else,

33:12.310 --> 33:13.220
but not this doll.

33:13.510 --> 33:14.380
Pick something else.

33:15.640 --> 33:16.420
Is it that important?

33:19.200 --> 33:21.290
Someone important gave it to me.

33:24.070 --> 33:25.380
So, you have someone important?

33:27.830 --> 33:29.050
Then forget about seeing Xiaowei.

33:30.160 --> 33:30.730
I...

33:32.480 --> 33:33.350
Miss Lu...

33:35.070 --> 33:35.900
Alright, Wuyi.

33:36.400 --> 33:37.700
Stop teasing Mr. Ji.

33:38.960 --> 33:39.730
Mr. Ji,

33:40.480 --> 33:42.420
we did work together.

33:44.790 --> 33:45.980
You helped us catch Xiaowei.

33:46.270 --> 33:47.500
I'll let you see him.

33:48.920 --> 33:49.700
But,

33:50.400 --> 33:52.910
remember you owe us a big favor.

33:53.030 --> 33:53.810
No problem.

34:12.550 --> 34:13.460
You scared me!

34:20.230 --> 34:20.860
Scared you?

34:21.110 --> 34:22.010
You scared me!

34:26.360 --> 34:27.580
Are you really helping Ji Ling

34:27.670 --> 34:28.570
and that big guy

34:29.000 --> 34:30.260
take Xiaowei to their sect?

34:32.070 --> 34:32.740
What else?

34:33.360 --> 34:34.860
Take you instead?

34:35.550 --> 34:36.690
You're not worth the bounty.

34:39.230 --> 34:40.980
My pretty lady will get mad.

34:43.480 --> 34:44.490
Which pretty lady?

34:45.890 --> 34:47.430
Like seeing flowers in the mist,

34:48.530 --> 34:49.760
even through the pouch,

34:49.760 --> 34:51.260
Miss Wu looks pretty.

34:54.190 --> 34:56.980
My head's full of Wu right now.

34:58.280 --> 35:00.090
Looks to me your head's misted.

35:01.220 --> 35:02.210
Is it?

35:03.190 --> 35:04.210
Don't forget our goal.

35:12.960 --> 35:13.610
A new demon?

35:25.280 --> 35:26.860
I know what you want to ask.

35:28.760 --> 35:30.300
Wangyan, you look upset.

35:31.110 --> 35:32.570
Something bothering you?

35:35.840 --> 35:37.610
So many people in Luo'an

35:37.670 --> 35:38.610
asked for love talismans.

35:39.230 --> 35:40.860
All these hexed people

35:41.280 --> 35:42.820
risk being cursed any time.

35:43.880 --> 35:45.820
You're worried how to fix it,

35:46.070 --> 35:46.570
right?

35:47.400 --> 35:49.210
You really know me best.

35:49.440 --> 35:50.740
It is strange.

35:51.480 --> 35:52.980
Xiaowei's been giving out talismans

35:53.000 --> 35:54.010
for over ten years.

35:54.510 --> 35:55.940
Those hexed people

35:56.400 --> 35:57.690
lived normal lives.

35:58.440 --> 35:59.270
Why did they suddenly

35:59.270 --> 36:00.570
tear the talismans,

36:00.880 --> 36:02.130
getting their hearts ripped out?

36:02.710 --> 36:04.210
Someone must be behind this.

36:24.840 --> 36:26.050
So many people tearing talismans,

36:26.400 --> 36:27.170
suffering the curse.

36:28.400 --> 36:29.460
Who's the mastermind

36:30.110 --> 36:30.860
behind all this?

36:34.480 --> 36:35.210
Speak!

36:46.840 --> 36:47.980
Do you sense demonic energy?

36:48.360 --> 36:49.010
Of course.

36:49.510 --> 36:50.980
Xiaowei's using magic again.

36:52.070 --> 36:53.380
That crazy, reckless fool!

36:55.590 --> 36:56.210
No.

36:57.320 --> 36:58.820
Another demon is here.

37:06.840 --> 37:07.420
Rude.

37:11.360 --> 37:12.870
I let the Dragon Deity down.

37:13.760 --> 37:15.070
I broke my vow.

37:16.030 --> 37:17.130
Go back and tell him

37:18.150 --> 37:19.460
to be on guard.

37:20.510 --> 37:21.300
That person...

37:23.360 --> 37:24.420
is truly terrifying.

37:25.550 --> 37:26.340
Who?

37:27.440 --> 37:28.610
A butterfly demon.

37:30.150 --> 37:31.130
A month ago,

37:33.190 --> 37:34.650
he came to Weimiao Pavilion for me.

37:48.280 --> 37:49.860
He said his name was Yuan Wuhuo,

37:51.400 --> 37:53.170
meaning "nothing gained."

37:57.550 --> 37:58.940
Yuan Wuhuo...

38:10.590 --> 38:11.610
Sir,

38:12.030 --> 38:13.650
are you here for a love talisman?

38:14.750 --> 38:16.530
I'm here to grant your wish.

38:17.640 --> 38:19.170
Quite confident.

38:20.230 --> 38:21.780
You've been looking for someone,

38:22.280 --> 38:23.650
and I know where they are.

38:24.710 --> 38:26.210
Then tell me,

38:26.480 --> 38:27.690
who am I looking for?

38:29.030 --> 38:30.460
You're looking for Wang Sheng.

38:40.590 --> 38:41.740
Nothing in this world

38:42.360 --> 38:43.900
comes for free.

38:45.510 --> 38:46.530
What do you want?

38:47.150 --> 38:47.980
What a coincidence.

38:49.000 --> 38:50.570
My name is

38:50.870 --> 38:51.570
Yuan...

38:52.550 --> 38:53.490
Wuhuo.
[*nothing gained]

38:54.480 --> 38:55.900
He made two demands.

38:56.710 --> 38:57.700
He wanted me to take back

38:57.700 --> 38:59.530
the nine-tailed power I lent the Dragon Deity,

39:00.360 --> 39:01.880
and to tell him

39:01.880 --> 39:03.690
how to reverse the love talisman's spell.

39:05.920 --> 39:06.940
But he didn't lie to me.

39:08.000 --> 39:10.010
He really helped me find Wang Sheng.

39:29.080 --> 39:30.010
What is that thing?

39:30.950 --> 39:33.300
How can it know everything?

39:37.670 --> 39:38.970
Heavenly Sticks.

39:41.670 --> 39:42.610
Heavenly Sticks?

39:44.070 --> 39:45.650
So this butterfly demon is something.

39:46.760 --> 39:47.420
Why?

39:48.030 --> 39:48.740
An immortal

39:49.320 --> 39:50.860
from thousands of years ago

39:51.000 --> 39:51.900
left that magical tool.

39:52.480 --> 39:54.260
It can see fate and destiny.

39:55.000 --> 39:55.460
However,

39:55.670 --> 39:57.690
prying into fate comes at a cost.

39:58.110 --> 39:58.940
Each divination

39:59.670 --> 40:01.010
must be paid for with one's own sacred power

40:01.510 --> 40:02.460
and lifespan.

40:04.190 --> 40:05.490
"Hard to come back.

40:08.670 --> 40:10.130
Hard to find again..."

40:16.000 --> 40:17.150
But the ancients said,

40:17.230 --> 40:18.460
fate cannot be revealed.

40:18.710 --> 40:20.300
So what the sticks can tell

40:20.440 --> 40:21.420
is only an approximation.

40:22.710 --> 40:24.050
That's why I came to the Wei mansion,

40:24.480 --> 40:26.210
never expecting fate to toy with me.

40:27.960 --> 40:28.650
Perhaps...

40:29.510 --> 40:31.210
this is heaven's punishment for you.

40:32.400 --> 40:33.650
You made so many lovers

40:33.820 --> 40:35.010
part as strangers,

40:35.400 --> 40:36.980
and the loveless wed as mates.

40:42.150 --> 40:43.820
I only helped those poor souls

40:43.840 --> 40:45.690
like myself.

40:47.000 --> 40:48.860
Their love hurt too much.

40:49.320 --> 40:50.050
You're wrong,

40:51.070 --> 40:51.740
Xiaowei,

40:52.880 --> 40:53.900
After a thousand years of cultivation,

40:54.480 --> 40:55.530
you still don't get it.

40:56.360 --> 40:57.300
Like people love flowers.

40:58.070 --> 40:58.860
In your hand,

40:59.670 --> 41:00.300
they're beautiful.

41:00.960 --> 41:01.980
On the branch,

41:02.510 --> 41:03.380
they're also beautiful.

41:04.510 --> 41:05.760
But those seeking talismans

41:05.960 --> 41:07.300
are like picking flowers by force,

41:08.110 --> 41:09.340
only making them wither,

41:10.510 --> 41:11.530
ending in tragedy.

41:13.800 --> 41:15.260
Yuan Wuhuo wanting you to take back your magic,

41:15.880 --> 41:16.690
I can understand.

41:17.500 --> 41:18.250
But he lured

41:18.250 --> 41:20.160
those hexed people to tear talismans,

41:20.800 --> 41:22.310
making them suffer the curse,

41:22.920 --> 41:23.820
why?

41:26.960 --> 41:28.010
I know his purpose.

41:29.280 --> 41:30.460
The Fox-Allure Spell in Luo'an

41:30.460 --> 41:31.170
isn't lifted yet.

41:31.920 --> 41:32.610
So,

41:33.480 --> 41:34.460
you can't take Xiaowei.

41:35.320 --> 41:36.690
Her staying won't help.

41:37.280 --> 41:39.050
She can't even lift her own spell.

41:39.550 --> 41:40.490
Then we really can't

41:41.150 --> 41:42.490
let a murderer walk away.

41:43.110 --> 41:43.980
Actually,

41:44.510 --> 41:46.640
I do know one power

41:46.880 --> 41:49.230
that can undo the spell's curse.

42:01.900 --> 42:02.700
Dragon Deity,

42:02.960 --> 42:03.780
please save us!

42:03.800 --> 42:04.820
We're under the Fox-Allure Spell!

42:05.710 --> 42:06.420
Please, Dragon Deity!

42:06.480 --> 42:06.980
Oh man,

42:07.000 --> 42:08.260
who spread the rumor

42:08.550 --> 42:10.000
that only the Dragon Deity's power

42:10.000 --> 42:10.570
can undo

42:10.630 --> 42:11.610
the Fox-Allure Spell's curse?

42:11.880 --> 42:12.490
Who knows.

42:13.000 --> 42:14.740
Everyone with a love talisman

42:15.030 --> 42:16.090
gathered here,

42:16.440 --> 42:17.210
stuck kneeling.

42:19.360 --> 42:20.050
What a headache.

42:22.400 --> 42:23.380
The Dragon Deity's power?

42:27.960 --> 42:29.460
Can it really cleanse the spell?

42:30.440 --> 42:32.750
The Dragon Deity's power can revive the dead,

42:32.960 --> 42:34.420
undo all spells and curses.

42:35.280 --> 42:36.090
However,

42:36.670 --> 42:38.900
I've heard some rumors lately.

42:39.110 --> 42:40.610
I don't know if they're true.

42:41.920 --> 42:42.820
You mean the rumor

42:43.920 --> 42:45.980
about the one worshiped by all,

42:46.280 --> 42:47.860
the last dragon son in the world,

42:48.880 --> 42:50.210
Chi Wen?

42:52.000 --> 42:52.780
What rumor?

42:54.190 --> 42:55.130
The rumor says

42:55.920 --> 42:57.340
Chi Wen...

42:57.800 --> 42:59.820
No longer has the Dragon Deity's power.

43:18.070 --> 43:18.740
Bai Ze.

43:20.920 --> 43:22.450
Master, you rarely summon me.

43:23.640 --> 43:24.460
What's it this time?

43:25.270 --> 43:26.380
After Xiaowei,

43:27.950 --> 43:29.250
Wu Zhiqi and Han Ba

43:29.710 --> 43:31.660
also broke their vows,

43:32.570 --> 43:33.350
taking back

43:33.350 --> 43:34.820
the power they lent me.

43:37.120 --> 43:37.870
In this Spirit-Binding Ring,

43:37.870 --> 43:39.540
only your power remains.

43:40.640 --> 43:42.100
There must be a schemer

43:43.120 --> 43:45.050
behind their sudden betrayal.

43:45.880 --> 43:46.650
So I need you

43:46.840 --> 43:47.900
to find them.

43:48.400 --> 43:49.130
I know.

43:50.030 --> 43:51.260
I've already found Xiaowei.

43:52.360 --> 43:53.050
Right now,

43:53.510 --> 43:54.940
she's hiding in the Wei mansion in Luo'an.

43:56.150 --> 43:56.860
Master,

43:57.440 --> 43:59.340
you no longer have the Dragon Deity's power.

43:59.670 --> 44:01.340
Please stay in the sect

44:02.150 --> 44:03.210
to be safe.

44:04.920 --> 44:05.740
So,

44:05.960 --> 44:07.580
now Chi Wen

44:07.670 --> 44:09.600
can only stay in the Dragon Deity Temple,

44:09.800 --> 44:11.590
under the sect's tight protection.

44:11.800 --> 44:14.100
He occasionally receives petitioners,

44:14.510 --> 44:17.210
but rarely ventures out,

44:17.800 --> 44:19.420
scared of being killed by demons.

44:21.070 --> 44:22.900
A dragon without its power

44:23.480 --> 44:24.740
still counts as a deity?

44:26.320 --> 44:27.780
So pitiful.

44:47.500 --> 44:48.660
♪It's your light♪

44:48.860 --> 44:50.740
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

44:50.900 --> 44:54.020
♪That set the night alight♪

44:54.380 --> 45:00.900
♪And lead me through the fight♪

45:02.660 --> 45:04.540
♪Jade in the lake, sand in my hand♪

45:04.980 --> 45:09.420
♪Let bitter seeds grow, let fate bloom♪

45:10.220 --> 45:11.900
♪Face in the mirror, veiled in mist♪

45:12.060 --> 45:17.460
♪Till snow has kissed dark hair to white♪

45:18.220 --> 45:23.620
♪Night lamp burning by the old table♪

45:25.940 --> 45:31.980
♪Stitch by stitch, mending moonlight♪

45:32.940 --> 45:35.100
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

45:35.380 --> 45:40.220
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

45:40.580 --> 45:42.900
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

45:43.100 --> 45:48.180
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

45:48.420 --> 45:50.420
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

45:50.700 --> 45:55.060
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

45:56.060 --> 46:03.020
♪Stay with me, let's gaze above♪

46:19.580 --> 46:22.540
♪Nowhere to rest, nowhere to hide♪

46:23.620 --> 46:27.020
♪Bare in body yet boundless inside♪

46:27.820 --> 46:30.340
♪Nothing to seek, nothing to erase♪

46:30.580 --> 46:33.660
♪Like water gone, like the formless moon♪

46:34.060 --> 46:36.380
♪Let every dream and wild desire♪

46:36.900 --> 46:41.300
♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪

46:41.540 --> 46:43.700
♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪

46:44.100 --> 46:49.060
♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪

46:49.300 --> 46:50.460
♪It's your light♪

46:50.660 --> 46:52.500
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

46:52.700 --> 46:55.820
♪That set the night alight♪

46:56.580 --> 47:06.020
♪And lead me sailing afar♪
